text.p: Trade continued active on Wednesday, USDA said. Steers and heifers were firm to $1.00 per cwt higher on a dressed basis delivered (paid on hot carcass weights), USDA said.
Dressed Basis Steers - Select and Choice 2-3 1200-1350 lbs mostly 116.00, few 115.00-115.50. ( weighted average 115.82 ).
Dressed Basis Heifers - Select and Choice 2-3 1100-1250 lbs mostly 116.00,few 115.00-115.50.(weighted average 115.70).
Slaughter steers and heifers 1.00 higher on a live basis. Demand and inquiry good, seller interest good.
Live basis sales - Equivalent 3 percent shrink delivered and FOB, some FOB 4% shrink.
Slaughter Steers - Select and Choice 2-3 1200-1300 lbs 72.00-72.50. Slaughter Heifers - Select and Choice 2-3 1100-1200 lbs 72.00-73.00, few early 70.50.
Confirmed - 13,500 Last Week - 30,800 Last Year - 7,200 Wk To Date- 48,400 Sm Pd Lst Wk- 44,900 Sm Pd Lst Yr- 66,500
